post_content: Stay Puft (Grape Gasoline x Marshmallow OG) is a premium indica strain delivering relaxing effects with sweet marshmallow and grape gasoline flavors. Hand-cultivated in our climate-controlled indoor facility.
Garlic Gravity (Garlatti x Zero Gravity) is a powerful indica strain with unique savory garlic notes and heavy relaxing effects. Perfect for evening use and deep relaxation.
Sherb Cream Pie (Ice Cream Cake x Sherb BX1) combines creamy dessert flavors with balanced hybrid effects. Sweet cream and berry notes with uplifting yet relaxing properties.
Skyworld Wafflez (Apple Fritter x Stuff French Toast) is our signature indica with breakfast pastry flavors. Rich apple and cinnamon notes with deeply relaxing effects.
Dirt n Worms (Gummy Worms x Quicksand) is a unique hybrid with earthy and sweet candy flavors. Balanced effects perfect for any time of day use.
White Apple Runtz delivers crisp apple flavors with the classic Runtz sweetness. Potent effects with uplifting and euphoric properties.
41 G (Gelato 41 x Gary Payton) is an F3 hybrid combining the best of both legendary strains. Creamy gelato flavors with balanced euphoric effects.
Melted Strawberries is a premium sativa strain with intense strawberry flavors and energizing effects. Perfect for daytime use and creative activities.
Triple Burger (GMO × Double Burger) is a potent indica with savory burger-like flavors. Heavy effects perfect for evening relaxation and appetite stimulation.
Peanut Butter Gelato (PB Cookies × Starfighter × SC × Gelato) combines nutty peanut butter flavors with creamy gelato sweetness. Balanced hybrid effects.
Kept Secret (Jealousy x Oreoz) is our mysterious indica strain with complex cookie and cream flavors. Deeply relaxing effects with subtle euphoria.
